\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
What if there is a state variable, show following the same steps that the
 HJB equation becomes: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\rho V\left(t,S,H\right)=U\left(c\left(X,S\right)\right)+V_{s}\mu_{s}+\lambda\left[V\left(t,S,L\right)-V\left(t,S,H\right)\right]+\dot{V},
\]

\end_inset

and by analogy: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
